WorldStage Newsonline– Vitafoam Nigeria Plc., Nigeria’s leading manufacturer of flexible, reconstituted and rigid foam products. It has the largest foam manufacturing and distribution network, which facilitates just-in-time delivery of its products throughout Nigeria has released its consolidated and separate financial statements for 3 months ended 31 December , 2020 (Q1) with a growth in revenue  to N8.666 billion from N5.984 billion in same period in 2019. Profit for the period grew by 35.72% to N1.112 billion from N819.674 million in same quarter in 2019.